'''Dragonstone''' [[gems]] are used in [[Crafting]], they are cut from [[uncut dragonstone]] with a [[chisel]], requiring 55 Crafting, and yielding 137.5 Crafting [[experience]]. Dragonstones are used to make dragonstone [[jewellery]] by using it on a [[furnace]] with a [[gold bar]] and a [[mould]].

[[Monster]]s with access to the [[rare drop table]] have a chance to drop cut dragonstones.

[[Dragonstone (Mage Training Arena)|Dragonstone]]s from the [[Mage Training Arena]] [[minigame]] are different, providing [[pizazz points]] when [[enchantment spells]] are used on them and they cannot be taken outside the [[Mage Training Arena#Enchanting Chamber|enchanting chamber]].

