===Magic===
Dragonstone jewellery is enchanted using [[Lvl-5 Enchant]], requiring 68 [[Magic]], 1 [[Cosmic rune]], 15 [[Earth rune]]s, 15 [[Water rune]]s along with the piece of dragonstone [[jewellery]]. Charged dragonstone jewellery is some of the few usable [[teleportation]] methods beyond level 20 up to level 30 [[Wilderness]] along with the [[pharaoh's sceptre]], [[grand seed pod]], [[royal seed pod]], [[slayer ring]], and [[ring of life]].
